devdoc.author: Eduardo Suarez Ojeda
devdoc.details: The Insurance Contract which represents the state of an insurance taken out by a hotel.

addSpcAddress(address).details: Updates the address of the general contract for security reasons.

deletePCR(bytes32).details: Updates the state of the PCR selected.

serializeInsurance().details: Returns all data of the insurance in an array of bytes.

updatePCR(bytes32,bytes32).details: Update the PCR selected and fires Sinister event if the result is positive.
